	<div class="columns">
	<div class="column">
		<p>
		Currently this poetry engine uses a topic modeling algorithm called latent dirichlet allocation (LDA) which sorts each poem into a set of topics based on their vocabulary. For each poem I look for another poem with the most similar topics. I also make sure that the poems look similar -- that they have a (relatively) similar number of lines and words per line. So your recommended poem has similar topics to your selected poem and visually looks about the same. 
		</p>
		<br />
		<p>
		I go into the algorithm more deeply on the <a href="../howitworks">about</a> page.
		</p>
	</div>
